			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "In order:\r\n\r\n- Steal Tusgront's Ring (without being spotted) after the conversation, but before he's in position to open the door (Short time window, might need turn based mode)\r\n- Discover the secret door via perception, then cast knock/lockpick it\r\n- Convince Tusgront to open the door for you, then just actually let him do it."
				},
