				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Tusgront's AD's for the few states he can be in infront of the Guildhall. In particular most of these are just there to confirm when he's done/tried to do an action, but the \"Stolen ring\" one is also there to prompt players that he's going to turn hostile if they approach the door and get caught now - as it wouldn't be obvious otherwise."
				}
			}
